NK040(thi)014:1: // zab don gcod kyi phung po mchod sbyin gdan thog
NK040(thi)014:2: gcig ma nyams su len pa'i rim pa bzhugs so
NK040(thi)014:3: // spyi don gnyis pa dngos gzhi nyams len gyi rim pa la bzhi ste /
NK040(thi)014:4: mngon par rtogs pa'i go rim bstan pa /
NK040(thi)014:5: nad gdon gzer bu'i gdam pa bstan pa /
NK040(thi)014:6: man ngag 'thor ba'i las tshogs bstan pa /
NK040(thi)014:7: spyi ching gal mdo'i rim pa bstan pa'o //
NK040(thi)014:9: dang po dbang bsdud zil gnon gyi rim pa /
NK040(thi)014:10: gnyis pa skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK040(thi)014:12: bzhi pa gsol ba gdab pa /
NK040(thi)014:16: dang po ni nan tan bya ba'i phyir skabs 'dir
NK040(thi)014:17: yang dbang bsdud zil gnon gyi rim pa gzhung ltar
NK040(thi)014:19: sa 'og sa steng sa bla gsum gyi bka' snang
NK040(thi)014:20: zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre thams cad 'dir 'dus shig
NK040(thi)014:21: / ces brjod pas lha 'dre thams cad 'ub kyis 'dus par bsgom /
NK040(thi)014:23: des dbang bsdud zil gnon song nas /
NK040(thi)014:24: rgyun du gces pa rnam brgyad ni /
NK040(thi)014:25: brten sa dkon mchog gsum po gces //
NK040(thi)014:26: snang srid snying rjes skyongs ba gces //
NK040(thi)014:28: gnyis pa skyabs su 'gro dgos pas /
NK040(thi)014:30: phatah gcig byas pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)014:31: skad cig gis mdun gyi nam mkha'i gnas su /
NK040(thi)014:32: pad+ma dang zla ba'i gdan la /
NK040(thi)014:33: ma cig lab kyi sgron ma la /
NK040(thi)014:34: grub thob gcod kyi brgyud pa rnams dang /
NK040(thi)014:35: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro chos skyong srung ma'i
NK040(thi)014:36: tshogs kyis bkra dpung nge 'od thibs se bskor nas
NK040(thi)014:39: thugs kyis dgongs nas bzhugs par sgom /
NK040(thi)014:40: phatah gcig gis rang nyid tha mal pa red par bsgom la /
NK040(thi)014:41: rang nyid dang lha 'dre kun gyis skyabs 'gro mgrin gcig tu byed par bsam zhing 'di skad do //
NK040(thi)014:42: gnas gdon lus gdon gnyis kyi gtsor byas nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad /
NK040(thi)014:43: bla ma la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK040(thi)014:44: sangs rgyas la chos la dge 'dun la ma cig
NK040(thi)014:45: lab kyi sgron ma la 'khor rigs bzhi mkha' 'gro
NK040(thi)014:46: ma rnams la grub thob gcod kyi brgyud pa rnams
NK040(thi)014:47: la rtogs ldan nyams kyi brgyud pa rnams la mkha'
NK040(thi)014:48: 'gro chos skyong srung ma'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams
NK040(thi)014:50: de ltar lan bdun tshar nas thun mong ma yin
NK040(thi)014:51: pa'i skyabs 'gro dang yan lag brgyad pa chab gcig
NK040(thi)014:54: gnyan sa 'dir gnas kyi lha 'dre dang //
NK040(thi)014:55: bdag la cho 'phrul ston pa'i lus gdon rnams //
NK040(thi)014:56: ma mi min ye shes mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)014:57: lab sgron khyed la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK040(thi)014:58: rang rig ye shes ston mdzad pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:59: bla ma rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK040(thi)014:60: dngos grub nges par ster mdzad pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:61: yi dam rnams la brtse gdung dam tshig ldan pa yis //
NK040(thi)014:62: mkha' 'gro rnams la bgegs dang bar chad zhi mdzad pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:63: chos skyong rnams la spangs rtogs phun sum tshogs pa yis //
NK040(thi)014:64: sangs rgyas rnams la zhi gyur 'dod chags bral ba yi //
NK040(thi)014:65: dam chos rnams la gang la phul na don che ba'i //
NK040(thi)014:66: dge 'dun rnams la gzhon nu'i tshul 'dzin yon tan ldan //
NK040(thi)014:67: 'jam dpal dbyangs la nges par snying rje bskyed pa yi //
NK040(thi)014:68: spyan ras gzigs la mthu stobs chen pos gdug pa 'dul //
NK040(thi)014:69: rdo rje bsnams la bdag sogs 'gro ba sems can rnams //
NK040(thi)014:70: ji srid snying po byang chub bar //
NK040(thi)014:71: khyed rnams la ni skyabs su mchi //
NK040(thi)014:72: khyed rnams la ni gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)014:73: khyed rnams la ni brten baca'o //
NK040(thi)014:75: phung po lnga po mchod par bzhes //
NK040(thi)014:76: sdig pa mi dge so sor bshags //
NK040(thi)014:77: 'gro ba'i dge la rjes yi rang //
NK040(thi)014:78: chos kyis 'khor lo bskor du gsol //
NK040(thi)014:79: mya ngan mi mda' gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)014:80: dge des sems can bde gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:81: rdzogs sangs rgyas su sems bskyed do //
NK040(thi)014:82: ces ma cig gis mdzad pa'i skyabs 'gro yan lag brgyad pa'o //
NK040(thi)014:83: gsum pa sems bskyed pa ni /
NK040(thi)014:84: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad kyi don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par bya /
NK040(thi)014:85: de'i ched du theg pa chen po'i gcod nyams su len par bya snyam du /
NK040(thi)014:87: sems can thams cad bde ba dang bde ba'i rgyu dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:88: sdug bsngal dang sdug bsngal gyi rgyu dang bral bar gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:89: sdug bsngal med pa'i bde ba dam pa dang mi 'bral bar gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:90: nye ring chags sdang gnyis dang bral ba'i btang snyoms la gnas par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:92: skyabs yul gyi lha tshogs rnams dgyes shing 'dzum pa'i tshul gyis /
NK040(thi)014:93: gdan khri dang bcas pa 'od du zhu nas /
NK040(thi)014:94: rang gi tshangs bug tu thim pa tsam gyis lus
NK040(thi)014:95: phyi nang gi sdig sgrib dam tshig chags nyams thams
NK040(thi)014:96: cad sangs kyi dag par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:98: bzhi pa gsol ba gdab pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK040(thi)014:99: dang po lha bskyed mchod bstod ni /
NK040(thi)014:100: swa b+ha wa shud+d+ha sarba d+har+m+aa swa b+ha wa shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK040(thi)014:101: bdag dang dngos po thams cad stong par gyur /
NK040(thi)014:102: stong pa'i ngang las rang gi spyi bor mda' gang tsam gyi steng du /
NK040(thi)014:103: pad+ma nyi ma zla ba'i gdan la /
NK040(thi)014:104: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo rtsa
NK040(thi)014:105: ba'i bla ma dang gnyis su med pa'i ma cig
NK040(thi)014:106: lab kyi sgron ma sku mdog gangs ri la nyi
NK040(thi)014:107: ma shar ba ltar dkar ba /
NK040(thi)014:108: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas gser gyi d+aa ma ru /
NK040(thi)014:109: g.yon dngul dkar gyi dril bu g.yer kha dkrol ba /
NK040(thi)014:110: sku la ras phrug dkar po'i ral ka mnab pa /
NK040(thi)014:111: dbu skra sil mas sku rgyab non pa /
NK040(thi)014:112: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil krung gi bzhugs pa /
NK040(thi)014:113: mtshan dang dpe byad 'od zer dang ldan par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:114: ma cig gi spyi bor pad zla nyi ma'i steng du /
NK040(thi)014:115: yum chen mo shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin ma gser gyi mdog 'dra ba /
NK040(thi)014:116: zhal gcig phyag bzhi ma g.yas kyi dang po na
NK040(thi)014:117: gser gyi rdo rje lnga pa thugs kar bsnams pa
NK040(thi)014:118: / 'og ma na shes rab kyi ral gri /
NK040(thi)014:120: 'og ma na shes rab kyi po ti bsnams pa /
NK040(thi)014:121: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil krung du bzhugs pa /
NK040(thi)014:122: ral pa thor tshugs lhag ma thur du grol ba /
NK040(thi)014:123: rin po che dang dar sna tshogs kyis spras pa /
NK040(thi)014:124: mtshan dang dpe byad 'od zer 'bar ba gcig tu bsam /
NK040(thi)014:125: ma cig gi g.yas su pad zla nyi ma'i steng
NK040(thi)014:126: du sangs rgyas bstan pa'i gtso bo sh+aakya thub pa
NK040(thi)014:128: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas sa non /
NK040(thi)014:130: chos gos ngur smrig gsol ba /
NK040(thi)014:131: mtshan dang dpe byad 'od zer 'dom gang dang bcas par bsgom /
NK040(thi)014:132: ma cig gis g.yon du 'jam dpal smra ba'i seng ge zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK040(thi)014:134: g.yon ut+pala'i khar shes rab kyi po ti bsnams pa /
NK040(thi)014:135: gser mdog ral pa spyi bor bcings pa /
NK040(thi)014:137: rin po che sna tshogs kyis brgyan cing dar sna lnga'i sham thabs can /
NK040(thi)014:138: sems dpa'i skyil krung gis bzhugs par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:139: yum sras de bzhi la mdun nas g.yas bskor du pad zla'i gdan la /
NK040(thi)014:144: skyo ston bsod nams bla ma /
NK040(thi)014:145: ma cig lab kyi sgron ma /
NK040(thi)014:157: slob dpon pra dz+ny+aa gu ru /
NK040(thi)014:160: rtogs ldan nam mkha' rdo rje /
NK040(thi)014:161: skyes mchog tshul khrims rgyal mtshan /
NK040(thi)014:162: mtshungs med chos kyi rdo rje /
NK040(thi)014:163: mkhas grub dz+ny+aa na ke tu /
NK040(thi)014:164: skyes mchog bsod nams dpal ba /
NK040(thi)014:169: mgon po nam mkha' rdo rje /
NK040(thi)014:186: rtsa ba'i bla ma sogs zhes sam /
NK040(thi)014:187: yang na man ngag don brgyud ltar na nam mkha' rgya mtsho'i rjes /
NK040(thi)014:197: grub thob gcod kyi brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams dang /
NK040(thi)014:198: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' bla ma yi
NK040(thi)014:199: dam mkha' 'gro chos skyong srung ma thams cad sprin
NK040(thi)014:200: gtib pa ltar bskor nas bzhugs pa'i spyi bor /
NK040(thi)014:201: mgrin pa +aah thugs kar h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas ye shes pa spyan drangs /
NK040(thi)014:202: badz+ra sa ma ya dza dza /
NK040(thi)014:203: dzahmh'u bam hoh gnyis su med par gyur par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:205: ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing //
NK040(thi)014:206: bdud sde dpung bcas mi zad 'jom mdzad lha //
NK040(thi)014:207: dngos rnams ma lus ji bzhin mkhyen gyur pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:208: yum chen 'khor bcas gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK040(thi)014:210: yang dag nyid du dag mod kyang //
NK040(thi)014:211: 'jig rten sri zhu'i tshul gyis ni //
NK040(thi)014:212: phyag dang zhabs gnyis bsil mdzod la //
NK040(thi)014:213: 'di nyid du ni bzhugs su gsol //
NK040(thi)014:216: mya ngan mi mda' thugs rje'i ngang //
NK040(thi)014:217: nyon mongs ma spangs gos pa med //
NK040(thi)014:218: ma chags rang bzhin dag pa yis //
NK040(thi)014:219: pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK040(thi)014:220: pad+ma ka ma la ye s+t+wam /
NK040(thi)014:223: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK040(thi)014:224: sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK040(thi)014:225: yid bzhin rin chen lta bu'i sku //
NK040(thi)014:226: bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)014:227: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK040(thi)014:228: ma skyes mi 'gags nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK040(thi)014:229: so so rang rig ye shes spyod yul ba //
NK040(thi)014:230: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)014:231: thabs mkhas thugs rjes sh+aakya'i rigs su 'khrungs //
NK040(thi)014:232: gzhan gyis mi thub bdud sde'i dpung 'joms pa //
NK040(thi)014:233: gser gyi lhun po lta bu mdzes pa'i sku //
NK040(thi)014:234: sh+aakya'i rgyal po khyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)014:235: gzhon nu'i sku lus 'chang ba po //
NK040(thi)014:236: ye shes sgron mes rab tu brgyan //
NK040(thi)014:237: 'jig rten gsum gyi mun sel ba //
NK040(thi)014:240: de nas nyer spyod lnga'i mchod cing /
NK040(thi)014:243: phung po khrol gyi zhig pas mchod pa'i sprin spungs du gyur /
NK040(thi)014:244: dri med yid du 'ong ba yis //
NK040(thi)014:245: lha rdzas dam pa'i mchod yon 'di //
NK040(thi)014:246: zhabs bsil me tog bdug spos dang //
NK040(thi)014:247: snang gsal dri chab zhal zas rol mo 'di //
NK040(thi)014:248: bla ma yum chen d+aak+ki'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK040(thi)014:249: 'gro ba'i don du mchod cing bzhes su gsol //
NK040(thi)014:250: badz+ra ar+g+ham pa t+yam nas shap+da bar brjod la /
NK040(thi)014:251: phatah lpags pa phyal gyis bting ba dbang chen gser gyi sa gzhir gyur /
NK040(thi)014:252: phatah khrag chil gyis byung bas dri bzang gi chur gyur /
NK040(thi)014:253: phatah sha nyil gyis spungs bas me tog gi tshom bur gyur /
NK040(thi)014:254: phatah gzugs khog ri rab tu gyur /
NK040(thi)014:255: phatah yan lag bzhi gling bzhir gyur /
NK040(thi)014:256: phatah nying lag thams cad gling phran brgyad du gyur /
NK040(thi)014:257: phatah mgo bo rnam par rgyal ba'i khang bzang du gyur /
NK040(thi)014:258: phatah mig gnyis nyi ma dang zla bar gyur /
NK040(thi)014:259: phatah so thams cad skar mar gyur /
NK040(thi)014:260: phatah rtsa rnams dpag bsam gyi ljon shing du gyur /
NK040(thi)014:261: phatah ba spu rnams tsan dan gyi nags tshal du gyur /
NK040(thi)014:262: phatah rgyu ma phyi yi lcags ri 'khor yug du gyur /
NK040(thi)014:263: phatah snying la sogs pa'i nang rol rnams yid bzhin
NK040(thi)014:264: gyi nor bu la sogs pa'i lha mi'i longs spyod
NK040(thi)014:265: phun sum tshogs pas gang bar gyur /
NK040(thi)014:266: sa gzhi spos chus byugs shing me tog sogs nas /
NK040(thi)014:267: tram gu ru rat+na man+dala pu tsa me g+ha sa
NK040(thi)014:268: mun tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye +aa h'u
NK040(thi)014:269: / zhes mchod cing bstod pa ni /
NK040(thi)014:270: ma chos dbyings rnam dag skye med dbyings kyi yum //
NK040(thi)014:271: 'gags med rtsa bral sems nyid don gyi yum //
NK040(thi)014:272: mtha' dbus med pa mtha' bral stong pa'i yum //
NK040(thi)014:273: ma yum chen chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)014:274: 'gyur ba med pa'i rdo rje'i sku sprul ma //
NK040(thi)014:275: dgos 'dod kun 'byung rin chen sku sprul ma //
NK040(thi)014:276: gdod nas dag pa pad+ma'i sku //
NK040(thi)014:277: phrin las sprul pa las kyi sku //
NK040(thi)014:278: ma yum chen sku lnga lhun grub ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)014:279: ma dang po lus srog bskyed pa'i ma //
NK040(thi)014:280: bar du zang zin byin pa'i ma //
NK040(thi)014:281: tha ma skye med ston pa'i ma //
NK040(thi)014:282: ma drin mo che la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)014:283: dri med rnam dag dam tshig mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)014:284: ye shes dpag med sna tshogs mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)014:285: chos nyid klong yangs thams cad mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)014:287: spangs rtogs mthar phyin sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)014:288: d+aak+ki yongs rdzogs sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)014:289: phatah spyi bo'i lha tshogs rnams kyis thugs ka nas
NK040(thi)014:290: 'od zer byung bas rang dang lha 'dre la phog
NK040(thi)014:291: pas lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig sgrib bag chags
NK040(thi)014:292: thams cad dag par bsam nas cung zad bzla /
NK040(thi)014:293: gnyis pa gsol ba gdab pa dngos ni /
NK040(thi)014:294: dbyangs dang bcas pas 'di skad do //
NK040(thi)014:295: phatah rang gi spyi gtsug tu ma cig lab kyi
NK040(thi)014:296: sgrol ma la 'khor grub thob gcod yul brgyud pa'i
NK040(thi)014:297: bla ma rnams kyis bskor nas bzhugs par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:298: gnas 'og min chos dbyings pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)014:299: yum chen shes rab phar phyin byin rlabs can //
NK040(thi)014:300: rje byin rlabs can la gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)014:301: rje byin rlabs can gyi byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)014:302: gnas bya rgod phung pa'i ri bo nas //
NK040(thi)014:303: bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa byin rlabs can //
NK040(thi)014:304: rje byin rlabs can la gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)014:305: rje byin rlabs can gyi byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)014:306: brag seng chen bsnol ba'i khri steng nas //
NK040(thi)014:307: 'jam dpal smra ba'i seng ge byin rlabs can //
NK040(thi)014:308: rje byin rlabs can la gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)014:309: rje byin rlabs can gyi byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)014:310: gnas g.yu lo bkod pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK040(thi)014:311: ma rje btsun sgrol ma byin rlabs can //
NK040(thi)014:312: rje byin rlabs can la gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)014:313: rje byin rlabs can gyi byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)014:315: mkha' 'gro su kha sid+d+hi byin rlabs can //
NK040(thi)014:316: rje byin rlabs can la gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)014:317: byin rlabs can gyi byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)014:318: gnas rgya gar chos kyi pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)014:319: rje btsun +aar+ya de ba byin rlabs can //
NK040(thi)014:320: rje byin rlabs can la byin rlabs can gyi gtsang la stod deng ri'i dgon pa na //
NK040(thi)014:321: pha dam pa rgya gar byin rje byin rlabs can
NK040(thi)014:322: la rje byin rlabs can gyi gnas dbus gtsang gnyis
NK040(thi)014:324: skyo ston bsod nams bla ma rje byin rlabs can
NK040(thi)014:325: la rje byin rlabs can gyi gnas zangs ri mkhar
NK040(thi)014:327: ma cig lab kyi sgron ma byin rje byin rlabs
NK040(thi)014:328: can la rje byin rlabs can gyi byin gnas snye
NK040(thi)014:329: mo khu yi ra ba nas //
NK040(thi)014:330: khu sgom chos kyi seng+ge byin rje byin rlabs can la gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)014:331: rje byin rlabs can gyi byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)014:332: gnas smad lung lcags sar gyi dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)014:333: pha dol pa zangs thal byin rlabs can //
NK040(thi)014:334: rje byin rlabs can la rje byin rlabs can gyi dpal chu bo ri yi dgon pa nas //
NK040(thi)014:335: rje rgya nag gcer bu byin rje byin rlabs can
NK040(thi)014:336: rje byin rlabs gnas rab grong se ba'i gling gang
NK040(thi)014:337: nas // sangs rgyas rab ston byin rlabs rje byin
NK040(thi)014:338: rlabs can la rje byin rlabs can gnas zal mo
NK040(thi)014:340: zal mo dge slong byin rje byin rlabs can rje
NK040(thi)014:341: byin rlabs can gnas kha rag mun song gi dgon
NK040(thi)014:342: pa nas // pha zhen med ras pa byin rje
NK040(thi)014:343: byin rlabs can rje byin rlabs gnas ri gang dpal
NK040(thi)014:345: sangs rgyas gnyan ston byin rje byin rlabs can rje
NK040(thi)014:346: byin rlabs can 'bangs pa bkra shis kyi dgon pa
NK040(thi)014:347: nas // d+har+m+aa seng ha byin rlabs rje byin rlabs
NK040(thi)014:348: can rje byin rlabs can gyi gnas gar bzhugs chos
NK040(thi)014:350: badz+ra seng+ha byin rje byin rlabs can rje byin rlabs can gnas kahthoga dpal gyi dben gnas su /
NK040(thi)014:351: pra dz+ny+aa gu ru byin rje byin rlabs rje byin
NK040(thi)014:352: rlabs can gnas dpal 'bar bkra shis dgon pa ru
NK040(thi)014:353: // rdo rje dpal ba byin rlabs can //
NK040(thi)014:354: rje byin rlabs can rje byin rlabs can gyi snang srid chos sku'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)014:355: nam mkha' rdo rje byin rlabs can //
NK040(thi)014:356: rje byin rlabs can rje byin rlabs can gyi dga' ldan gnam stong ri khrod nas //
NK040(thi)014:357: shi la ke tu byin rlabs rje byin rlabs can
NK040(thi)014:358: la rje byin rlabs can gyi spang ka ma chos

NK040(thi)014:452: sems dbyer med rtogs par dag snang phyogs med 'byong
NK040(thi)014:453: par na tsha bogs su thon par byin rkyen ngan
NK040(thi)014:454: lam du slong bar byin gnyan sa ri khrod 'grim
NK040(thi)014:455: par 'gro don mtha' ru phyin par gcod yul nyams
NK040(thi)014:456: su len par lha 'dre'i 'gro don nus par sku
NK040(thi)014:457: 'gyur ba med par gsung 'gags pa med pa byin
NK040(thi)014:458: thugs 'khrul ba med par byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)014:459: lus shag ma shig ma byin gyis sems khral ma
NK040(thi)014:460: khrol mar nyams 'ar ma 'ur ma snang ba ban

NK040(thi)014:462: sa ri khrod 'di ru 'dug sa 'di ru byin
NK040(thi)014:463: gyis rlobs // myur ba nyid du byin da lta nyid du byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)014:464: phatah phatah ma cig brgyud pa dang bcas pa'i sku
NK040(thi)014:465: las zag med ye shes kyi bdud rtsi dkar la
NK040(thi)014:466: dwangs pa khra la la bab pas bdag gi spyi
NK040(thi)014:467: gtsug tshangs bug du mar byung bas las dang nyon
NK040(thi)014:468: mongs pa'i sdig sgrib bag chags thams cad chu lam
NK040(thi)014:469: dang 'og sgo sen phrag nas mar bud nas zhabs
NK040(thi)014:470: dbang chen gser gyi sa gzhi'i zhabs su las kyi
NK040(thi)014:471: gshin rje sogs lan chags sha mkhon bu lon gyi
NK040(thi)014:472: mgron rnams kyi khar 'ub 'ub sib sib du thim
NK040(thi)014:473: par bsam / phatah tshogs zhing rnams las 'od zer
NK040(thi)014:474: byin rlabs sprin dpung lta bur 'phros 'gro drug sems
NK040(thi)014:475: can dang snang zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre rnams la
NK040(thi)014:476: phog pas de rnams kyi las dang nyon mongs pa'i
NK040(thi)014:477: sdig sgrib bag chags thams cad sang gis dag par
NK040(thi)014:478: par bsam / bsam / phatah nad pa la lan chags 'jal ba'i dmigs pa spyi tsam du /
NK040(thi)014:479: phatah bdag gzhan gyi sdig sgrib bkrus pa'i khu ba
NK040(thi)014:480: ngo bo bdud rtsi'i rnam par 'dod yon longs spyod
NK040(thi)014:482: lus gdon nad bdag lan chags sha mkhon bdag po kun gyi khar song bas /
NK040(thi)014:484: ngom zhing tshim nas lan chags sod /
NK040(thi)014:485: bu lon byang sha mkhon dag /
NK040(thi)014:486: gnod sems zhi nas phan sems dang ldan par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:487: phatah rang gi nad gnod sha khrag dang bcas pa
NK040(thi)014:488: dag nas lus khru ma phus btab zin 'o mas
NK040(thi)014:490: gsum pa dbyings rig bsre ba ni /
NK040(thi)014:491: swa b+ha was stong par sbyongs /
NK040(thi)014:492: stong pa'i ngang las rang lus stong ra khang stong
NK040(thi)014:493: ka ba gcig pa lta bu'i lte ba nas spyi
NK040(thi)014:494: gtsug gi bar du rtsa dbu ma snyug dong kha
NK040(thi)014:496: yar sne spyi gtsug tshangs pa'i bu gar zug pa /
NK040(thi)014:497: mar sne lte 'og sor bzhi'i thad du yod pa'i nang du /
NK040(thi)014:498: rang gi rnam par shes pa'i ngo bo thig le dkar la dmar ba'i mdangs chags pa /
NK040(thi)014:499: bya ma gsar gyi sgong nga lta bur snum la 'dril ba dkar la 'tsher ba /
NK040(thi)014:500: nam tho rangs kyi skar chen shar bar ltar 'phar
NK040(thi)014:501: ling ling byed pa 'od zer kun tu 'phro bar
NK040(thi)014:502: bsgom / phatah byas pa tsam gyi yar lte bar 'phar ba bsam /
NK040(thi)014:507: phatah ma cig thugs kar thim par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:508: ma cig brgyud pa'i bla ma dang bcas pa nam mkha' la 'ja' yal ba ltar song bar bsgom /
NK040(thi)014:510: dbyings dang rig pa nam mkha' gsum dbyer med stong
NK040(thi)014:511: pa gcig tu gyur pa'i ngang la ci gnas su
NK040(thi)014:512: bzhag go // bzhi bsre nam mkha' sgo 'byed gces /
NK040(thi)014:517: ma cig dang bzhi'i shes pa bsre bar bya'o //
NK040(thi)014:518: shes pa bzhi'i bsre lugs ni /
NK040(thi)014:519: nad pa 'khor khal rta gsum gyi shes pa thig
NK040(thi)014:520: le dkar la dmar ba'i mdangs chags pa'i tshul du
NK040(thi)014:521: bla ma'i gsang gnas kyi shes pa'i ngo bo la
NK040(thi)014:522: bsre / bla ma dang grogs chos mthun gyi shes pa thugs kar bsre /
NK040(thi)014:525: ro thams cad bla ma'i ro la bstim /
NK040(thi)014:526: 'khor thams cad dang bla ma dang sgar pa kun
NK040(thi)014:527: gyi shes pa rnams ro gong bzhin du rang rang
NK040(thi)014:528: la basre'o // ro bsres dang dbyings bsres sdeb na chun cig tu chod pa'i gnad do //
NK040(thi)014:529: de yang ma cig gis zhal nas //
NK040(thi)014:530: nam mkha' sgo 'byed re re de //
NK040(thi)014:531: dbang bskur phal gyi do zla min //
NK040(thi)014:533: des bzhi bsre nam mkha' sgo 'byed song /
NK040(thi)014:534: lnga pa bdud rtsi dkar 'gyed ni /
NK040(thi)014:538: sbyangs byed kyi yi ge 'bru gsum dang gnyis /
NK040(thi)014:539: byin gyis rlabs byed yi ge 'bru gsum bdud rtsi bsgyur ba dang gsum ste /
NK040(thi)014:541: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro la //
NK040(thi)014:542: tshogs mchod dngos grub blang bar gces //
NK040(thi)014:543: pha ma sems can thams cad la //
NK040(thi)014:544: chos dang zang zing sbyin pa gces //
NK040(thi)014:546: skye med kyi ngang las rtog pa gcig byung ma thag tu /
NK040(thi)014:547: phatah gcig byas pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)014:548: stong pa chos kyi sku las gzugs skur bzhengs nas /
NK040(thi)014:549: rang gi rig pa'i ngo bo rje btsun ma sku
NK040(thi)014:550: mdog dmar po phyag na gri gug dang thod khrag
NK040(thi)014:552: phatah phatah phatah de'i mdun du rang gi ro de
NK040(thi)014:553: che la tsho ba snum la mdzes pa dkar la
NK040(thi)014:554: 'tsher ba stong gsum nam mkha'i khams dang mnyam pa
NK040(thi)014:555: gcig tu gyur / phatah rje btsun ma'i gri gug
NK040(thi)014:556: gis bem po de'i dpral mdo na gcig brgyab pas
NK040(thi)014:557: gcig tu gyur / / shag gis bshags nas lpags
NK040(thi)014:558: pa sil gyis bshus shing mchog phur bzhi har gyi
NK040(thi)014:559: gcig tu gyur / / btsug / lpags pa de'i
NK040(thi)014:560: yan lag bzhi 'then nas lhu tshigs dang pus tshigs
NK040(thi)014:561: bzhi bcad nas yan lag bzhi lpags pa'i glor 'byar
NK040(thi)014:562: gcig tu gyur / / btsug / bar bsgom / phatah gcig byas pas /
NK040(thi)014:563: lpags de phyal gyis bting bas gling bzhi khyab par bsgom /
NK040(thi)014:565: yan lag bzhi phyogs bzhi zug nas /
NK040(thi)014:566: yan lag bzhi'i kha na lpags pa de dmar thang nge yod par bsgom /
NK040(thi)014:568: rje btsun ma'i gri gug gi rtse mos bem po
NK040(thi)014:569: de blangs nas lpags pa'i thog tu 'phang ste rjes
NK040(thi)014:570: su gri gug gi ro la gcig brgyab pas dmar
NK040(thi)014:572: phatah gti mug sha yi ri bo /
NK040(thi)014:573: phatah 'dod chags khrag gi rgya mtsho /
NK040(thi)014:574: phatah zhe sdang rus pa'i gram khrod chen por gyur par bsam la ngag tu /
NK040(thi)014:576: ces lan gsum brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)014:577: rang nyid rje btsun ma'i thugs ka nas gzab yig
NK040(thi)014:578: ram dmar po gcig 'phros pas sha khrag la phog
NK040(thi)014:579: nas me 'bar te dngos po ma dag pa thams
NK040(thi)014:580: cad thal ba bun gyis song bar bsam /
NK040(thi)014:581: yam sngo skya gcig spros pa las rlung byung nas
NK040(thi)014:582: mes bsregs zin gyi thal ba ma lus pa bkrus
NK040(thi)014:583: par bsam / kham sngon po gcig spros pas chu
NK040(thi)014:584: byung bas rlung gis gtor zin gyi thal ba rnams
NK040(thi)014:585: ma lus pa bkrus par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:586: mal du dwangs ma yod pa de /
NK040(thi)014:587: +aahmh'u gsum du gyur pa de yar gcig thog na gcig brtsegs nas yod par bsgom /
NK040(thi)014:590: brjod pa tsam gyis 'od du zhu ba las zag
NK040(thi)014:591: med ye shes kyi bdud rtsi rgya mtsho chen po
NK040(thi)014:592: nam mkha' dang mnyam par bsam la /
NK040(thi)014:593: phatah mgron tshan bzhi po mdun du rim bzhin 'khod nas yod par dmigs la /
NK040(thi)014:594: dang po srid zhu'i mgron la 'bul ba ni /
NK040(thi)014:596: phyogs bcu dus gsum na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang
NK040(thi)014:597: byang chub sems dpa' grub thob gcod yul brgyud pa'i
NK040(thi)014:599: nyan thos rang rgyal rnams dang /
NK040(thi)014:600: chos sku kun tu bzang po man chad rtsa ba'i bla ma yan chad /
NK040(thi)014:601: rig 'dzin brgyud pa dang bcas pa rnams dang /
NK040(thi)014:602: yi dam mkha' 'gro chos skyong srung ma 'khor dang bcas pa rnams la mchod do //
NK040(thi)014:604: 'khor ba ma stong gi bar du bdag gi lus
NK040(thi)014:605: 'di kun tu bzang po'i mchod sprin du gyur nas
NK040(thi)014:606: / dkon mchog gsum la mchod cing mnyes par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:607: bdag sogs sems can thams cad la mchog thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa stsal du gsol /
NK040(thi)014:608: phatah lha tshogs rnams dgyes pa'i skan sgra dang bcas pas gsol bar bsam /
NK040(thi)014:609: phatah gcig gis lha tshogs rnams dgyes nas mi dmigs pa'i ngang la bzhag go //
NK040(thi)014:610: phatah gcig gis lhag ma gsal bar bskyed nas /
NK040(thi)014:611: gnyis pa yon tan mgron la 'bul ba ni /
NK040(thi)014:612: phatah gcig byas pa tsam gyis yang ro snga ma ltar bskyed la /
NK040(thi)014:614: ces lan gsum brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)014:615: dkar gsum mngar gsum zhal zas ro mchog brgya dang
NK040(thi)014:616: ldan pa stong gsum nam mkha' dang mnyam par bsam
NK040(thi)014:617: / stong gsum mi 'jed kyi bdag po dpal tshangs
NK040(thi)014:618: pa dang brgya byin rgyal po chen po sde bzhi
NK040(thi)014:619: / la sogs pa / gtsang rigs kyi dpal mgon
NK040(thi)014:620: bdun cu rtsa lnga 'khor dang bcas pas rnams la
NK040(thi)014:621: / la sogs pa / mchod do // 'bul lo //
NK040(thi)014:623: ci 'dod pa'i longs spyod du gyur nas dgyes shing tshim par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:624: khyed rnams kyi sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srung ba dang /
NK040(thi)014:625: sems can thams cad la bde skyid 'byung bar mdzad du gsol /
NK040(thi)014:627: lha tshogs rnams dgyes par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:628: phatah gcig gis gong bzhin mi dmigs pa dang /
NK040(thi)014:630: lan gsum byas pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)014:631: rin po che'i mchod sdong chen po nam mkha' dang mnyam par gyur /
NK040(thi)014:632: rang rang gi ci ltar mos pa'i tshogs su gyur
NK040(thi)014:633: pa 'di nyid bsngo zhing 'bul ba'i gnas ni gnas
NK040(thi)014:634: yul chen po gzhi yi bdag po sogs bka' yi
NK040(thi)014:635: lha ma srin sde brgyad rnams dang /
NK040(thi)014:636: 'gro ba drug gi sems can rnams la sbyin no //
NK040(thi)014:637: so so ci 'dod pa'i longs spyod du gyur nas /
NK040(thi)014:638: 'khor ba ma stong gis bar du sems can thams cad skye ba /
NK040(thi)014:651: la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral bar gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:652: tshe dang bsod nams dpal dang 'byor pa grags pa
NK040(thi)014:653: dang longs spyod ci 'dod pa'i bde skyid dpal 'byor
NK040(thi)014:654: phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par myur du sangs
NK040(thi)014:657: dgyes nas so so'i gnas su song nas sangs rgyas par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:658: phatah gcig gi gong bzhin dmigs la /
NK040(thi)014:659: bzhi pa lan chags mgron la 'bul ba ni /
NK040(thi)014:660: phatah gcig byas pa tsam gyis ro sngar ltar bsam la /
NK040(thi)014:661: +aahmh'u lan gsum byas pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)014:662: 'dod yon gyi tshogs su gyur nas rang rang gi
NK040(thi)014:663: ji ltar mos pa'i tshogs su gyur pa 'di nyid
NK040(thi)014:664: bsngo zhing sbyin pa'i gnas ni /
NK040(thi)014:665: gnas gdon lus gdon gnyis kyis gtsor byas /
NK040(thi)014:666: bdag cag gis tshe rabs grangs med kyi bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu /
NK040(thi)014:671: ma bdud rgyal mo 'khor dang bcas pa rnams dang /
NK040(thi)014:674: sa bdag dang klu srin dal yams nad kyi bdag po bdag mo /
NK040(thi)014:675: rims kyi bdag po bdag mo /
NK040(thi)014:676: grib kyi bdag po bdag mo /
NK040(thi)014:677: lan chags kyi bdag po bdag mo rnams la ster ba yin pas bu lon sod /
NK040(thi)014:679: sha mkhon byang nas khyed rnams sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang rin po che thob par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:681: 'dod yon gyis tshim nas sangs rgyas par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:682: phatah gcig gis lhag ma yang gsal ste /
NK040(thi)014:683: lnga pa dbang dman la sbyin pa ni /
NK040(thi)014:684: lhag ma gsal ba de nyid /
NK040(thi)014:685: +aahmh'uh lan gsum gyis byin gyis rlabs la /
NK040(thi)014:686: lhag ma rnams 'gro ba rigs drug gi nang nas khas zhan cing dbang chung ba /
NK040(thi)014:691: la sogs pa lhag ma la dbang ba rnams la sbyin no //
NK040(thi)014:692: zha bo rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:693: long ba ye shes kyi spyan dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:694: lkug pa tshangs pa'i dbyangs dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:695: 'on pas chos kyi sgra thos par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:696: rje bla ma'i thugs dgongs rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:697: rgyal ba mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:698: dam can thugs dam bskang gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:699: rigs drug 'dod pas tshim gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:700: bu lon lan chags byang gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:701: so sor ci 'dod pa'i longs spyod du gyur nas
NK040(thi)014:702: myur du sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang rin po che
NK040(thi)014:705: mgron bzhi po de thams cad rje btsun ma sku mdog dmar mo'i tshul du bsgom la /
NK040(thi)014:706: de rnams kyi sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs can
NK040(thi)014:707: thams cad yi ge +aahmh'u gis tshul du gyur nas
NK040(thi)014:708: / rang gi gnas gsum du thim nas sku gsung
NK040(thi)014:709: thugs kyi dngos grub ma lus pa thob par bsam
NK040(thi)014:710: / mo // des lnga pa bdud rtsi dkar 'gyed de song ngo //
NK040(thi)014:712: spyi bor ma cig lab kyi sgron ma grub thob
NK040(thi)014:713: gcod kyi brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams kyis bskor nas
NK040(thi)014:715: thog mar gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK040(thi)014:716: yum chen shes rab phar phyin la sogs pa //
NK040(thi)014:717: skye med chos kyi sku la gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)014:718: rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:719: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams la 'jam dpal smra ba'i seng+ge la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:720: rgyal sras 'phags pa rnams la seng lding nags kyi sgrol ma la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:721: 'jigs pa brgyad skyob rnams la mkha' 'gro su kha sid+d+hi la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:722: ma brgyud mkha' 'gro rnams la rje btsun +aar+ya de ba la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:723: 'dzam gling skyes mchog rnams la pha gcig dam pa rgya gar la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:724: rgya gar grub chen rnams la skyo ston bsod nams bla ma la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:725: bod yul skyes mchog rnams la ma cig lab kyi sgron ma la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:726: ye shes mkha' 'gro rnams la khu sgom chos kyi seng+ge la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:727: skye med don rtogs rnams la pha cig dol pa zang thal la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:728: skyes mchog don grub rnams rje btsun rgya nag gcer bu la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:729: rnal 'byor 'khrul zhig rnams la sangs rgyas rab ston la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:730: mkhas grub chen po rnams la sangs rgyas dge slong rnam dag la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:731: tshul khrims mthar phyin rnams la sangs rgyas sum b+ha ras chen la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:732: brtul zhugs grub pa rnams la grub thob sangs rgyas gnyan ston la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:733: chos kyi spyan ldan rnams la gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)014:734: ras pa chos kyi seng+ge la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:735: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rnams la rje btsun badz+ra seng+ha la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:736: dam chos smra ba rnams la slob dpon pra dz+ny+aa gu ru la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:737: rtogs ldan dam pa rnams la rje btsun badz+ra sh+r+ai la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:738: 'gro ba'i mgon po rnams la rtogs ldan nam mkha' rdo rje la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:739: don gnyis grub pa rnams la skyes mchog tshul khrims rgyal mtshan la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:740: bskyed rdzogs brtan thob rnams la mtshungs med chos kyi rdo rje la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:741: stong nyid mthar phyin rnams la drin chen dz+ny+aa na ke tu la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:742: mkhas btsun dam pa rnams la rat+na sh+r+ai kun dga' 'bum pa sogs //
NK040(thi)014:743: gcod kyi bka' babs rnams la pun+ye lak+sha rdo rje 'od zer sogs //
NK040(thi)014:744: bya btang rnal 'byor rnams la rgyal mtshan seng+ge ga ga badz+ra sogs //
NK040(thi)014:745: rnal 'byor rtogs ldan rnams la ga ga ma ti ka la badz+ra sogs //
NK040(thi)014:746: bstan 'dzin skyes mchog rnams la dbang drag rgya mtsho chos skyong rgya mtsho sogs //
NK040(thi)014:747: 'khrul zhig dbang phyug rnams la klong gsal snying po chos nyid rgya mtsho sogs //
NK040(thi)014:748: rdzogs chen rnal 'byor rnams bkra shis phun tshogs nam mkha' rgya mtsho sogs //
NK040(thi)014:749: snyan brgyud 'dzin pa pad+ma rin chen 'ju bla gsang sngags sogs //
NK040(thi)014:750: gcod kyi grub thob rnams la pad+ma chos dbyings sangs rgyas grags pa sogs //
NK040(thi)014:751: bkab babs lung zin rnams nam mkha' chos skyong 'jigs med bsam gtan sogs //
NK040(thi)014:752: 'khrul rtogs tshar gcod kun bzang rnam rgyal dkon mchog bla ma sogs //
NK040(thi)014:753: snyigs dus 'gro mgon rnams d+har+m+aa s+aa ra rdo rje lags bshad sogs //
NK040(thi)014:754: 'gran bral skyes chen rnams la drin chen rtsa ba'i bla ma la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:755: grub thob gcod brgyud rnams la gnyan sa ri khrod 'grim pa la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:756: mched grogs chos mdzad rnams la yi dam mkha' 'gro sde lnga la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:757: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la chos skyong ma mgon
NK040(thi)014:758: lcam dral bka' srung dam can rnams la thar pa'i
NK040(thi)014:759: lam ston rnams la phan bde'i 'byung gnas rnams la
NK040(thi)014:760: 'phags pa'i dge 'dun rnams la bdag sogs mkha' mnyam
NK040(thi)014:762: ma rigs 'khrul pa sangs par byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)014:763: gzung 'dzin mdud pa grol bar byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)014:764: sgrib gnyis bag chags dag par byin smon 'jug sems
NK040(thi)014:765: bskyed 'byung bar byin pha rol phyin drug rdzogs par
NK040(thi)014:766: rkyen ngan grogs su 'char bar byin snang srid chos
NK040(thi)014:767: skur rtog par stong nyid snying rje 'byong bar bdag
NK040(thi)014:768: don chos sku rtogs par gzhan don gzugs sku 'byung
NK040(thi)014:769: bar don gnyis phun sum tshogs par byin gyis rlobs
NK040(thi)014:770: // zhes dang gonga du dkar 'gyed skabsa ltar /
NK040(thi)014:771: ma cig brgyud pa dang bcas pa'i sogs byin rlabs 'bebs sbyong dang dbyings rig bsre /
NK040(thi)014:773: stong pa'i ngang las rang gi lus stong ra khong stong sogs nas /
NK040(thi)014:774: ma cig thugs kar thim par bsam bar brjod /
NK040(thi)014:776: phatah rang gzhan gyi ro de che la tsho ba snum la mdzes shing yid du 'ong ba /
NK040(thi)014:777: dri dang ro phun sum tshogs pa 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad gang bar gyur /
NK040(thi)014:778: phatah de'i mdun du rang gi rnam par shes pa'i ngo bo de gshin rje a wa glang mgo /
NK040(thi)014:782: nga rgyal rngam pa dred kyi mgo bo can /
NK040(thi)014:783: gzhan yang stag gzig la sogs pa gcan gzan sna tshogs kyi mgo brnyan can /
NK040(thi)014:784: thog pa de rnams kyis ro gtub par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:785: phatah gti mug sha yi ri bo /
NK040(thi)014:786: phatah 'dod chags khrag gi rgya mtsho /
NK040(thi)014:787: phatah zhe sdang rus pa'i gram khrod chen po gcig gyur par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:788: phatah phatah phatah gshin rje de rnams kyis skad gdangs
NK040(thi)014:789: chen pos stong gsum nam mkha'i khyab tshad kyi lha
NK040(thi)014:791: sa 'og sa steng sa bla'i lha 'dre sde brgyad
NK040(thi)014:792: thams cad 'ub 'ub 'dus par bsam nas 'di skad
NK040(thi)014:794: gtso bo gdon chen bco brgyad /
NK040(thi)014:795: byis pa'i gdon chen bco lnga /
NK040(thi)014:800: mtho srid pa'i rtse mo man chad /
NK040(thi)014:801: dma' na rag dmyal khams yan chad /
NK040(thi)014:802: mtho nam mkha'i lha bran man chad /
NK040(thi)014:804: pe dkar rgyal po man chad /
NK040(thi)014:805: yul 'dre sa srin 'khyams po yan chad /
NK040(thi)014:806: snang zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre thams cad sha khrag dga' ston la 'dir 'dus shig /
NK040(thi)014:808: khyad par du'ang gnyan khrod chen po 'di na gnas pa'i dkar po lha yi sde tshan /
NK040(thi)014:809: nag po bdud kyi sde tshan /
NK040(thi)014:810: dmar po btsan gyi sde tshan /
NK040(thi)014:811: khra bo gza' yi sde tshan /
NK040(thi)014:813: phyug po klu yi sde tshan /
NK040(thi)014:815: pho mo ma ning gi sde tshan du gtogs pa'i
NK040(thi)014:816: snang zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre thams cad sha khrag
NK040(thi)014:819: khyad par du'ang bdag gam ch+gee'i phung po khams dang skye mched la /
NK040(thi)014:820: dang po nad kyi sna 'dren pa /
NK040(thi)014:821: bar du gdon gyi tshang bca' ba /
NK040(thi)014:822: tha ma nad la mi phan pa byed pa'i pho gdon rgyal po /
NK040(thi)014:836: kha yi nang gi dbug 'phrog pa /
NK040(thi)014:837: khog pa'i nang gi srog gcod pa'i gdon bgegs bdud
NK040(thi)014:838: dang log par 'dren pa thams cad sha khrag gi
NK040(thi)014:841: khyad par du'ang gnyan khrod chen po 'di'i phu mda'
NK040(thi)014:842: nyin srib la gnas pa'i lha 'dre bka' la 'khu
NK040(thi)014:844: mgo skor rjes snyogs byed pa'i lha 'dre gong ral
NK040(thi)014:845: 'khyams gsum 'jab rgyug log gsum byed pa'i lha 'dre
NK040(thi)014:849: dngos grub mi ster ba byed pa'i lha 'dre thams
NK040(thi)014:850: cad sha khrag gi dga' ston la 'dir 'dus shig
NK040(thi)014:852: kye 'dus shig sogs jo bo rje'i gsung khyad par can 'dir sbyar /
NK040(thi)014:854: gong ltar bos pa'i tshan gsum po thams cad 'dus par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:855: de tsam bos nas ci sbyin na /
NK040(thi)014:857: bdag cag rnams kyi lha 'dre khyed rnams 'bod nas ci sbyin ci ster zer na /
NK040(thi)014:858: bdag cag rnams kyi spyi bo'i gtsug man chad rkang mthil yan chad /
NK040(thi)014:872: dbugs dang tshe srog bkrag dang gzi mdangs /
NK040(thi)014:873: khams dang skye mched bcu gnyis la sogs pa rnams ster ba yin pas /
NK040(thi)014:881: phatah steng 'ja' 'od las grub pa'i gur khang nang du /
NK040(thi)014:882: gza' mchog chen po r+aa hu la mgo dgu pa mgo lus med par mig gis gang ba /
NK040(thi)014:883: steng zhal bya rog gi mgo gcig tu yod pa /
NK040(thi)014:884: phyag gnyis sbrul zhag dang rwa yi mda' gzhu 'geng ba /
NK040(thi)014:887: gza' phran bye ba dung phyur /
NK040(thi)014:888: bka' yi lha srin sde brgyad /
NK040(thi)014:889: steng gdon gza' yi rigs tshogs dang bcas pa rnams
NK040(thi)014:890: kyis bdag gzhan gyi sha khrag rus gsum 'di la
NK040(thi)014:896: phatah bar lha khang bya 'dab gsum pa'i nang du /
NK040(thi)014:897: rgyal po pe har gser thul can glang po che la zhon pa /
NK040(thi)014:901: las byed p+aa tra pu tra brgya /
NK040(thi)014:903: phyag gtsang phyag brnyan che ba pe har /
NK040(thi)014:906: srin mo dam sri nag mo /
NK040(thi)014:908: bar gdon rgyal 'gong gi rigs kyi tshogs dang bcas
NK040(thi)014:909: pa rnams kyi bdag cag gi sha khrag rus gsum
NK040(thi)014:916: phatah 'og rgya mtsho chen po sngo mer gyi gang ba'i nang du /
NK040(thi)014:917: klu nag po dur ba mgo dgu pa /
NK040(thi)014:918: phyag na chu gri thogs pa /
NK040(thi)014:919: de la klu chen brgyad klu phran bye ba dung phyur /
NK040(thi)014:921: nya dang lcong mo la sogs 'og gdon klu'i rigs
NK040(thi)014:922: kyi tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyis bdag gi sha
NK040(thi)014:923: khrag rus gsum 'di la zo zhig sogs /
NK040(thi)014:924: phatah khyad par du yul khams 'dir gnas pa'i btsan gyi sde tshogs ma mo'i sde tshogs /
NK040(thi)014:930: srin mo ro sgye khur ba /
NK040(thi)014:931: lu ba tsha rims kyi bdag po bdag mo /
NK040(thi)014:932: stong gsum nad yams kyi bdag po bdag mo /
NK040(thi)014:933: snang zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre rnams la bdag cag
NK040(thi)014:934: rnams kyi sha khrag rus gsum ster ba yin pa
NK040(thi)014:935: zo zhig sogs / phatah yod na yod tshad kyi
NK040(thi)014:936: lha 'dre rnams kyis bdag gzhan rnams kyi sha khrag
NK040(thi)014:938: sha la za re ba rnams kyis sha zo /
NK040(thi)014:939: khrag la 'thung re ba rnams kyis khrag 'thung /
NK040(thi)014:940: lpags la gyon re ba rnams kyis lpags pa gyon /
NK040(thi)014:941: so so'i 'dod dgu so so'i bsam dgu skyid dga'
NK040(thi)014:942: longs spyod che chung pham rgyal med par gyur cig
NK040(thi)014:943: / phatah phatah bsdu na gong gi steng nam mkha' nas 'di bar bzhag go //
NK040(thi)014:944: spyir rigs drug gi sems can rnams kyi glud du bsngo /
NK040(thi)014:945: sgos drin chen pha ma'i glud du bsngo /
NK040(thi)014:946: yang sgos rtsa ba'i bla ma'i glud du bsngo /
NK040(thi)014:947: khyad par du lha 'dre khyed rnams la gzan du ster ba yin pas zo zhig sogs /
NK040(thi)014:948: phatah bdag gi lus 'di bram zi skye ba bdun
NK040(thi)014:949: pa'i sha khrag tu byin gyis rlab pa yin pas
NK040(thi)014:950: khyed rnams kyis longs spyod pa tsam gyis khams gsum
NK040(thi)014:952: rigs drug gi sdug bsngal dang bral /
NK040(thi)014:953: sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang rin po che thob nas /
NK040(thi)014:954: sems can ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral bar byed pa yin /
NK040(thi)014:955: ma grol ba rnams grol ba byed pa yin /
NK040(thi)014:956: dbugs ma dbyung ba rnams dbugs dbyung bar byed pa yin /
NK040(thi)014:957: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa yongs su
NK040(thi)014:958: mya ngan las 'da' bar byed pa yin pas zo
NK040(thi)014:965: lha 'dre thams cad dga' zhing mgu nas /
NK040(thi)014:966: hab dir gyis bye'u chung chu la rub pa bzhin hab di ri ri zos 'thung /
NK040(thi)014:967: ngom zhing dgyes nas yod tshad zos /
NK040(thi)014:968: khyag tshad khur nas dga' ya le mgu zhing tshim nas bu lon sod /
NK040(thi)014:970: 'gras shing 'khon pa thams cad 'dum ci bsgo ba'i
NK040(thi)014:971: phrin las sgrub par khas blangs te thams cad rjee
NK040(thi)014:972: btsun mar sangs rgyas par bsam /
NK040(thi)014:974: phatah re dang mgron theb re sprad pa'i brgya rtsa brgyad byed do //
NK040(thi)014:975: de ltar byas pa'i yon tan ni /
NK040(thi)014:977: lus kyi mchod sbyin re re de //
NK040(thi)014:978: tshogs bsags mang pos do zla med //
NK040(thi)014:984: chos kyi mchod sbyin brjod las 'das //
NK040(thi)014:990: ro snga ma ltar bsam la /
NK040(thi)014:991: mgo brnyan can rnams kyi phyag na mtshon cha sna
NK040(thi)014:992: tshogs thogs te ro de gtsab res mi thob thob
NK040(thi)014:993: byed nas / lus gdon rnams kyis skad ngan tsi ri ri 'don cing /
NK040(thi)014:994: snang srid kyi bka' yi lha ma srin sde brgyad
NK040(thi)014:995: rnams kyang 'ub 'ub 'dus nas bkag mi thub thub
NK040(thi)014:996: byed par bsam la 'di skad do //
NK040(thi)014:998: khyod snang zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre rnams //
NK040(thi)014:1000: nam mkha' gang ba'i lha dmag 'dus //
NK040(thi)014:1001: bar snang gang ba'i gnyan dmag 'dus //
NK040(thi)014:1002: sa gzhi gang ba'i klu dmag 'dus //
NK040(thi)014:1003: sems 'gyu ba dngos med stong pa 'di //
NK040(thi)014:1004: 'dre khyod bas ngas kyang mthong ba med //
NK040(thi)014:1005: rab mdzes bdag gi phung po 'di //
NK040(thi)014:1006: 'dre khyod la mkho bas bdag gis sbyin //
NK040(thi)014:1007: bdag cag sha khrag gzugs phung la //
NK040(thi)014:1008: sha za hab sgra di ri ri //
NK040(thi)014:1009: khrag 'thung myig pa kyu ru ru //
NK040(thi)014:1010: rus 'cha' so sgra khrigs se khrig /
NK040(thi)014:1011: lha ba rkang 'jib chems se chem //
NK040(thi)014:1012: lpags pa gos gyon lhabs se lhab /
NK040(thi)014:1013: phatah khog stod ya bdud rgyal pos khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1014: ya bdud rgyal po tshim gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1015: khog smad ma bdud rgyal mos khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1016: ma bdud rgyal mo tshim gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1017: sked pa klu bdud nag pos khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1018: klu bdud nag po tshim gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1019: mgo bo gza' bdud mgo dgus khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1020: gza' bdud mgo dgu tshim yan lag gnyan chen sde bzhis khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1021: gnyan chen sde bzhi nang cha snang srid lha 'dres khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1022: snang srid lha 'dre tshim mchin pa smug po bdud kyis khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1023: bdud kyi sde tshogs glo ba dmar po btsan gyis khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1024: btsan gyi sde tshogs pho ba khra bo gza' yis khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1025: gza' yi sde tshogs don snying pe har rgyal pos khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1026: pe har rgyal po mcher pa mo gdon bsen gyis khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1027: mo gdon bsen mo mkhal ma klu gdon sa bdag khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1028: klu gdon sa bdag tshim rgyu ma lam gyi lha 'dres khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1029: lam gyi lha 'dre lpags pa 'di bse rag 'gong pos khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1030: bse rag 'gong po srog rtsa 'chi bdag gshin rjes khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1031: 'chi bdag gshin rje tshim phyi sha phyi yi lha 'dres khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1032: phyi yi lha 'dre nang sha nang gi lha 'dres khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1033: nang gi lha 'dre tshim gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1034: bar sha bar gyi lha 'dres khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1035: bar gyi lha 'dre tshim khyod snang zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre rnams //
NK040(thi)014:1036: sha 'dod rnams kyis sha khyer cig /
NK040(thi)014:1037: sha yi sa bdag tshim khrag 'dod rnams kyis khrag khyer la //
NK040(thi)014:1038: khrag gi klu rnams tshim rus 'dod rnams kyis rus pa khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1039: rus pas gnyan rigs tshim mdangs kyis bsen mo tshim
NK040(thi)014:1040: bkrag gi rgyal 'gong tshim khyed ring ba rnams kyis
NK040(thi)014:1041: rlon pa khyer // mi ring rnams kyis btsos la zo //
NK040(thi)014:1042: sha tshil ci 'dod gang dga' gyis //
NK040(thi)014:1043: ci za gyis la ci khyag khyer //
NK040(thi)014:1044: bsngosa pa bzhin du tshim gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1045: bu lon lan chags byang gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1046: rnam bzhi'i mgron du gyur pa la //
NK040(thi)014:1047: tshad med lus sbyin 'di bsngosa pas //
NK040(thi)014:1048: longs spyod ldan zhing tshogs rdzogs nas //
NK040(thi)014:1049: sngon chad 'khor ba thog med kyi //
NK040(thi)014:1050: bu lon 'brel thag chod gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1051: lan chags sha 'khon byang gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1052: khyed rnams dga' mgu yi rang zhing //
NK040(thi)014:1053: bsam sbyor ngan pa rab zhi nas //
NK040(thi)014:1054: zag med stong nyid snying rje'i rgyud brlan cing //
NK040(thi)014:1055: rnam mkhyen rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas myur thob shog /
NK040(thi)014:1056: phatah re byas pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)014:1057: lha 'dre thams cad 'dus nas hab thob ling gis btang nas zos pa bsam /
NK040(thi)014:1060: de ltar dmigs pa gong bzhin byed nas /
NK040(thi)014:1061: phatah brgya rtsa brgyad brjod pa yin no //
NK040(thi)014:1063: de nas bde sdug btang len ni /
NK040(thi)014:1064: mdun gyi nam mkha'i gnas su pad+ma dang zla ba'i gdan la /
NK040(thi)014:1065: ma cig lab kyi sgron ma 'od zer nyi ma
NK040(thi)014:1066: 'bum shar ba'i gzi brjid che ba gcig bsgom la
NK040(thi)014:1067: / ma cig gis thugs ka nas 'od zer lcags kyu lta bu grangs med par mar 'phros pas /
NK040(thi)014:1068: 'gro ba rigs drug na gnas pa'i sems can thams cad dang /
NK040(thi)014:1069: khyad par zas kha lag gi 'brel tshad kyi sems
NK040(thi)014:1070: can thams cad bsngo dgos yid la dran tshad ma
NK040(thi)014:1071: nam mkhas khyab tshad sems can rnams kyi rnam par
NK040(thi)014:1072: shes pa 'od kyi thig le re re gyur nas
NK040(thi)014:1073: / ma cig gi thugs ka'i 'od zer lcags kyu
NK040(thi)014:1074: rnon pos yar drangs thugs chos nyid kyi klong du
NK040(thi)014:1075: / thim par gyur / phatah phatah phatah gnyan khrod
NK040(thi)014:1076: chen po 'dir gnas pa'i snang zhing srid pa'i lha
NK040(thi)014:1077: 'dre rnams kyi rgyud la yod pa'i sdig sgrib bag
NK040(thi)014:1078: chags thams cad rang la smin par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1079: phatah rang gi dkar po dge ba'i rtsa ba chos
NK040(thi)014:1080: dang zang zing gi sbyin pa thams cad lha 'dre
NK040(thi)014:1081: rnams la smin par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1082: phatah lha 'dre rnams kyi gnod cing gdug pa'i ngan sems zhi nas /
NK040(thi)014:1083: bsam pa byang chub kyi sems dang ldan nas myur
NK040(thi)014:1084: du sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang rin po che thob
NK040(thi)014:1085: par gyur cig / phatah phan bde ma lus kun la 'bul //
NK040(thi)014:1086: phan bdes nam mkha' gang bar shog /
NK040(thi)014:1087: sdug bsngal ma lus bdag la 'dus //
NK040(thi)014:1088: sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho skem par shog /
NK040(thi)014:1089: phatah phatah phatah lan gsum brjod do //
NK040(thi)014:1091: sems can thams cad la chos kyi sbyin pa de
NK040(thi)014:1092: dag gis don shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin
NK040(thi)014:1093: pa mngon sum du rtog par bsam la /
NK040(thi)014:1094: bdag nyid skad cig gi ma cig lab kyi sgron
NK040(thi)014:1095: ma sku mdog dkar mo gzi dmangs dang ldan pa'i
NK040(thi)014:1096: thugs kar +aahdakara po 'od dang ldan pa dang /
NK040(thi)014:1097: rang gi spyi bor yum chen mo sku mdog ser
NK040(thi)014:1098: mo gtso ma'i mdog lta bu zhal gcig phyag bzhi
NK040(thi)014:1099: pa zhal nang du gyu ba'i thugs kar +aahsera po
NK040(thi)014:1100: de nyid kyi mthar ga te'i sngags kyis g.yon du
NK040(thi)014:1103: stong pa'i ngang las phyi snod kyi 'jig rten thams
NK040(thi)014:1104: cad 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi zhing khams su
NK040(thi)014:1105: gyur / nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad chos sku rgyal ba yum chen mo'i skur gyur /
NK040(thi)014:1106: sgrar grags tshad thams cad ga te'i sngags sgra 'ur ti ri ri sgrogs par bsgom /
NK040(thi)014:1107: lha 'dre rnams gnod cing gdug rtsub ngan pa'i sems zhi nas /
NK040(thi)014:1108: yum chen shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma'i don mngon sum du rtogs par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1109: don mngon sum du rtogs nas lha 'dre rnams kyis
NK040(thi)014:1110: dus gcig tu sngags sgra 'ur 'ur bzlas par bsgom
NK040(thi)014:1112: ga te ga te pa ra ga te pa ra sam ga te bo d+hi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK040(thi)014:1115: chos rnams thams cad rgyu las sogs /
NK040(thi)014:1118: dus gsum rgyal yum dgongs don rtogs par shog /
NK040(thi)014:1120: pha dam pa'i rtags bstod sogs gsol 'debs gang rung 'dir 'don /
NK040(thi)014:1122: gzer bu gdam pa ma dang sprod //
NK040(thi)014:1124: nad gdon gzer bu'i gdam pa dgos pa byung na
NK040(thi)014:1125: byed las 'og tu zhib pas gang dgos skabs dang
NK040(thi)014:1128: spyi don bdun pa gtor gzhong ma 'di la don bzhi'i ston pas /
NK040(thi)014:1129: dang po las mkhan bskyed pa ni /
NK040(thi)014:1130: phatah gcig byas pas yang ro snga ma ltar rang
NK040(thi)014:1131: gzhan gyi ro de che la tsho ba bsnum la
NK040(thi)014:1132: mdzes shing yid du 'ong ba 'jig rten gyi khams
NK040(thi)014:1135: rang gi rnam par shes pa'i ngo bo rje btsun
NK040(thi)014:1136: ma sku mdog dmar mo gri gug can gcig tu
NK040(thi)014:1137: gyur par bsgom / gnyis pa ka p+aa la bskyed pa ni /
NK040(thi)014:1139: kam kam kam brjod pa tsam gyis thod pa'i sgyed pu gsum du gyur /
NK040(thi)014:1140: rang gi thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum kha dog lnga dang ldan pa gcig spros pas /
NK040(thi)014:1141: thod gsum gyi khar phog pas 'od du zhu ba las /
NK040(thi)014:1142: ka p+aa la yangs shing rgya che ba blos khyab tshad gcig du bsgom /
NK040(thi)014:1143: phatah gcig byas pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)014:1144: gri gug gis rtse mos ro blang ste ka p+aa
NK040(thi)014:1145: la'i nang du 'phangs nas rjes su gri gug gis
NK040(thi)014:1146: ro la gcig brgyab pas dmar nyob kyis song nas
NK040(thi)014:1147: / gti mug sha yi ri bo /
NK040(thi)014:1149: zhe sdang rus pa'i gram khrod chen po stong gsum 'jig rten gyi khams gang bar gyur /
NK040(thi)014:1152: brjod pa tsam gyis ka p+aa la'i zhabs kyi yam las rlung byung ram la phog /
NK040(thi)014:1153: ram las me 'bar bas ka p+aa la dros te
NK040(thi)014:1154: khol nas dngos po ma dag pa thams cad sbu
NK040(thi)014:1156: dwangs ma'i bdud rtsi'i steng du yi ge +aahmh'u gsum 'od du zhu ba las /
NK040(thi)014:1157: zag med ye shes kyi bdud rtsir gyur nas /
NK040(thi)014:1158: ka p+aa la stems kyis gang bar dmigs /
NK040(thi)014:1159: phud rlangs pa yar chad pa las rje btsun ma
NK040(thi)014:1160: sku mdog dmar mo thod zhal 'dzin pa grangs med
NK040(thi)014:1161: du gyur nas / g.yas skor du gar stabs khyug khyug byed pa gcig tu gyur /
NK040(thi)014:1162: gsum pa ka p+aa la'i che yon ni /
NK040(thi)014:1163: ma cig gi zhal gdam bco brgyad las /
NK040(thi)014:1165: phyi snod 'jig rten gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1166: nang bcud sems can gtor mas bkang //
NK040(thi)014:1167: skye 'chi bral ba'i mchod pa bzhes //
NK040(thi)014:1168: gtor gzhong du phyi nam mkha' yangs pa'i nang 'byung
NK040(thi)014:1169: bzhi yi gtor mas bkang rang gsal rang dag mchod
NK040(thi)014:1170: pa bzhes // bka' pha rol phyin pa'i gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1171: sa bcu dag pa'i gtor mas bkang //
NK040(thi)014:1172: myang 'das chen po'i mchod bka' rdzogs pa chen po'i gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1173: theg pa brgyad kyi gtor mas ma 'dres yongs rdzogs mchod pa bzhes //
NK040(thi)014:1174: kun gzhi yangs pa'i gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1175: rnam shes tshogs brgyad gtor mas 'phel 'grib bral ba'i mchod pa rang sems gnyug ma'i gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1176: lus ngag yid gsum gtor mas brjod du med pa'i mchod pa bzhes //
NK040(thi)014:1177: skye ba med pa'i gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1178: rig pa tshor myong gtor mas bkang //
NK040(thi)014:1179: 'gyu ba rang grol mchod pa chos sku dag pa'i gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1180: gzugs sku rnam gnyis gtor mas bkang //
NK040(thi)014:1181: thugs rjes 'gro don mchod pa stong pa nyid kyi gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1182: snang ba dkar dmar gtor mas snang med chen po mchod pa rang rgyud dag pa'i gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1183: gnyis med gdams ngag gtor mas ngos bzung med pa'i mchod pa chos nyid dag pa'i gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1184: bde gsal chen po'i gtor mas dngos 'dzin bral ba'i mchod pa rang lus rgyal ba'i gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1185: rang sems skye med gtor mas re dog med pa'i mchod pa ka p+aa la yi gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1186: sha khrag rus gsum gtor mas 'dzin chags bral ba'i mchod pa bzhes //
NK040(thi)014:1187: rin chen snod kyi gtor gzhong du //
NK040(thi)014:1188: dkar gsum mngar gsum gtor mas bkang //
NK040(thi)014:1189: ro brgya ldan pa'i mchod gtor bzhes //
NK040(thi)014:1190: phatah des ka p+aa la'i che yon rdzogs nas /
NK040(thi)014:1191: bzhi pa mchod pa dngos ni /
NK040(thi)014:1192: bdud rtsi dkar la dmar ba'i mdangs chags pa rgya mtsho tsam du bskyed la /
NK040(thi)014:1194: rdo rje 'chang chen man chad dang //
NK040(thi)014:1195: rtsa ba'i bla ma yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1196: lus mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bsngosa pas //
NK040(thi)014:1197: bsngosa pa bzhin du tshim gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1198: bsam pa bzhin du 'grub gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1199: yum chen sher phyin man chad dang //
NK040(thi)014:1200: yi dam lha tshogs yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1201: lus mchod sbyin gtor ma bsngosa pa bzhin du bsam
NK040(thi)014:1202: pa bzhin du kun tu bzang po man chad dang
NK040(thi)014:1203: // 'jag ma'i srin bu yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1204: lus mchod sbyin gtor ma bsngosa pa bzhin bsam pa bzhin du 'grub sh+aakya thub pa man chad dang //
NK040(thi)014:1205: dmyal khams bco brgyad yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1206: lus mchod sbyin gtor ma bsngosa pa bzhin du bsam
NK040(thi)014:1207: pa bzhin du sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro man chad dang
NK040(thi)014:1208: // sha za shugs 'gro yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1209: lus mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bsngosa pa bzhin du
NK040(thi)014:1210: tshim bsam pa bzhin du chos skyong ma mgon man
NK040(thi)014:1211: chad dang // ging chen ging chung yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1212: lus mchod sbyin gtor ma bsngosa pa bsam pa bzhin du 'grub lha srin sde brgyad man chad dang //
NK040(thi)014:1213: the'u rang spun dgu yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1214: lus mchod sbyin bsngosa pa bzhin bsam pa bzhin du 'grub tshangs pa brgya byin man chad dang //
NK040(thi)014:1215: nam mkha'i lha bran yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1216: lus mchod sbyin gtor ma bsngosa pa bzhin du tshim
NK040(thi)014:1217: bsam pa bzhin du bi na ya ka man chad
NK040(thi)014:1218: dang // sa bdag lto 'phye yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1219: lus mchod sbyin sha khrag bsngosa pa bzhin du tshim
NK040(thi)014:1220: bsam pa bzhin du 'grub ri dbang rgyal po man
NK040(thi)014:1221: chad dang // mtsho sman phyug mo yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1222: lus mchod bsngosa pa bsam pa pe har rgyal po man chad dang //
NK040(thi)014:1224: lus mchod bsngosa pa bsam pa srin mo nag rul man chad dang //
NK040(thi)014:1225: grong yul 'dre mo yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1226: lus mchod sbyin bsngosa pa bzhin bsam pa pho sri mgo skya man chad dang //
NK040(thi)014:1227: mo sri rkang skya yan lus mchod bsngosa pa bsam
NK040(thi)014:1228: pa gzhon sri dar ma man chad chung sri kha
NK040(thi)014:1230: lus mchod bsngosa pa bsam pa the'u rang gre bo gre mo man chad dang //
NK040(thi)014:1231: bse rag 'gong po yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1232: lus mchod bsngosa pa bsam pa snang srid lha 'dre man chad dang //
NK040(thi)014:1233: gnyan sa'i lha 'dre yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1234: lus mchod bsngosa pa bzhin bsam pa gnas gdon lus gdon man chad dang //
NK040(thi)014:1235: bag la nyal ba yan chad la //
NK040(thi)014:1236: lus mchod bsngosa pa bsam pa gtor ma 'di bsngosa
NK040(thi)014:1237: yon tan gyis bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams
NK040(thi)014:1238: // lus la bde ba rnyed gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1239: ngag la nus pa 'bar gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1240: sems la rtogs pa 'char gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1241: mchog gi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK040(thi)014:1242: sarba dz+ny+aa na lo ka ga na tsakra la kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK040(thi)014:1243: ces 'bul gtor snying gzugs ma dang /
NK040(thi)014:1246: sha khrag sbyin btang bgyis pa 'di //
NK040(thi)014:1247: spyir 'gro drug yongs kyi glud du bsngo //
NK040(thi)014:1248: dgos drin chen pha ma'i glud du bsngo //
NK040(thi)014:1249: yang dgos rtsa ba'i bla ma'i glud du bsngo //
NK040(thi)014:1250: thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas myur thob shog phatah na mo /
NK040(thi)014:1251: bla ma dam pa'i thugs dgongs rdzogs gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1252: rgyal ba mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1253: dam can thugs dam bskang gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1254: rigs drug 'dod pa tshim gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1255: lha srin sde brgyad tshim gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1256: bu lon lan chags byang gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1257: rnam bzhi'i mgron du gyur pa la //
NK040(thi)014:1258: tshad med lus sbyin 'di bsngosa pas //
NK040(thi)014:1259: longs spyod ldan zhing tshogs rdzogs nas //
NK040(thi)014:1260: thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas myur thob shog /
NK040(thi)014:1261: phatah phatah phatah de nas bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK040(thi)014:1263: bde legs mchog gi rnyed thob de //
NK040(thi)014:1264: rtsa ba'i bla ma yin par ma shes nas //
NK040(thi)014:1265: dngos grub gzhan du btsal ba de //
NK040(thi)014:1266: ma sprul pa'i sku la mthol lo bshags //
NK040(thi)014:1267: rang sems rtsa ba chod pa de //
NK040(thi)014:1268: chos sku yin pa ma shes nas //
NK040(thi)014:1269: sangs rgyas gzhan du btsal ba de //
NK040(thi)014:1270: ma sprul pa'i sku la mthol lo bshags //
NK040(thi)014:1271: rnam rtog rang bzhin shar ba de //
NK040(thi)014:1272: skye med yin pa ma shes pas //
NK040(thi)014:1273: gnyen po gzhan du btsal ba de //
NK040(thi)014:1274: ma sprul pa'i sku la sems nyid yid bzhin nor bu de //
NK040(thi)014:1276: 'bad rtsol gzhan du byas pa de //
NK040(thi)014:1277: ma sprul pa'i sku la nga bdag rtsa ba chod pa de //
NK040(thi)014:1278: nyams len yin par ma shes pa //
NK040(thi)014:1279: lha 'dre gzhan du btsal ba de //
NK040(thi)014:1280: ma sprul pa'i sku la lha 'dre sems kyi 'dzin pa de //
NK040(thi)014:1281: cho 'phrul yin par ma shes pas //
NK040(thi)014:1282: nyams kyi bya ra byed pa de //
NK040(thi)014:1283: ma sprul pa'i sku la gsum ldan rtsa ba'i bla ma de //
NK040(thi)014:1284: skyabs gnas yin pa ma shes pas //
NK040(thi)014:1285: mos gus phul snying chung ba de //
NK040(thi)014:1286: ma sprul pa'i sku la 'di phyi bde legs ji snyed pa //
NK040(thi)014:1287: rtsa ba'i bla ma 'byung ba la //
NK040(thi)014:1288: dngos grub gzhan du rtsal ba de //
NK040(thi)014:1289: ma sprul pa'i sku la dngos 'byor yid sprul mchod pa de //
NK040(thi)014:1290: tshogs gnyis rdzogs par ma shes pas //
NK040(thi)014:1291: rlom sems ser sna byas pa de //
NK040(thi)014:1292: ma sprul pa'i sku la zab mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs gral de //
NK040(thi)014:1293: gsang gnas yin pa ma shes pas //
NK040(thi)014:1294: nyams grib can dang 'grogs pa de //
NK040(thi)014:1295: ma sprul pa'i sku la zhal zas tshogs gnyis longs spyod de //
NK040(thi)014:1296: dngos grub yin pa ma shes pas //
NK040(thi)014:1297: log lta can la spel ba de //
NK040(thi)014:1298: ma sprul pa'i sku la brtse gdung 'dres pa'i mched grogs de //
NK040(thi)014:1299: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro yin pa ma shes nas //
NK040(thi)014:1300: nyams pa'i khong khro shes pa de /
NK040(thi)014:1301: ma sprul pa'i sku la tshul khrims rnam dag dri med de //
NK040(thi)014:1302: thar lam yin par ma shes nas //
NK040(thi)014:1303: 'chal ba'i mngon lkog shor ba de //
NK040(thi)014:1304: ma sprul pa'i sku la khams gsum sems can thams cad kun //
NK040(thi)014:1305: pha ma yin par ma shes nas //
NK040(thi)014:1306: sems can gzhan la gnod pa de //
NK040(thi)014:1307: ma sprul pa'i sku la 'dzin zhes chags pa che ba de //
NK040(thi)014:1308: lta ngan yin par ma shes nas //
NK040(thi)014:1309: rtag tu re ba byed pa de //
NK040(thi)014:1310: ma sprul pa'i sku la man ngag bdud kyi gcod yul 'di //
NK040(thi)014:1311: gsang sngags yin par ma shes nas //
NK040(thi)014:1312: rgyal khams yongs la spel ba de //
NK040(thi)014:1313: ma sprul pa'i sku la chags med lus sbyin gtong ba de //
NK040(thi)014:1314: tshogs gnyis yin pa ma shes nas //
NK040(thi)014:1315: rang lus gces 'dzin byas pa de //
NK040(thi)014:1316: ma sprul pa'i sku mthol lo bshags so mi min mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)014:1317: gnong ngo 'gyod do grub thob gcod kyi brgyud //
NK040(thi)014:1318: sbyang ngo bsal lo dpa' bo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK040(thi)014:1319: chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang du mthol lo bshags //
NK040(thi)014:1320: don dam skye med ngang du bzod par gsol //
NK040(thi)014:1321: rnam dag bde chen ngang du dag gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1322: bdag dang 'gro drug sems can rnams //
NK040(thi)014:1323: tshogs rdzogs sgrib pa byang nas kyang //
NK040(thi)014:1324: myur du sangs rgyas thob par shog /
NK040(thi)014:1328: de nas bsngo ba smon lam gyi 'jug bsdu ba la /
NK040(thi)014:1331: bdag gzhan kun gyi dus gsum du //
NK040(thi)014:1333: de bzhin zag bcas zag pa med //
NK040(thi)014:1334: de dag kun la yi rang ngo //
NK040(thi)014:1335: yi rang byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK040(thi)014:1336: tshogs kyi lam dang sbyor ba'i lam //
NK040(thi)014:1337: mthong ba'i lam dang sgom pa'i lam //
NK040(thi)014:1338: bla na med pa khya par lam //
NK040(thi)014:1339: byang chub bar chad med pa'i lam //
NK040(thi)014:1340: bar chad med par 'jug par shog /
NK040(thi)014:1341: bar chad med par 'jug nas kyang //
NK040(thi)014:1342: ji srid 'khor ba ma stong bar //
NK040(thi)014:1343: stong nyid dam pa thob par shog /
NK040(thi)014:1344: phatah de nas smon lam ni /
NK040(thi)014:1345: phatah bdag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis //
NK040(thi)014:1346: bdag dang 'gro drug sems can rnams //
NK040(thi)014:1347: pha rol phyin drug rdzogs byas nas //
NK040(thi)014:1348: rnam mkhyen rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas myur 'grub shog /
NK040(thi)014:1349: dge ba 'di yi myur du bdag /
NK040(thi)014:1350: chos sku yum chen 'grub gyur nas //
NK040(thi)014:1351: 'gro ba gcig kyang ma lus pa /
NK040(thi)014:1352: thams cad de yi sa la 'god par shog /
NK040(thi)014:1354: bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa yis //
NK040(thi)014:1355: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas //
NK040(thi)014:1356: lam bsgrod byang chub mchog thob nas //
NK040(thi)014:1357: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK040(thi)014:1358: skye ba med las gzugs sku 'char //
NK040(thi)014:1359: 'gro rnams bde la bkod mdzad ma //
NK040(thi)014:1360: yum chen shes rab pha rol phyin ma yi //
NK040(thi)014:1361: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK040(thi)014:1362: thugs las 'khrungs pa'i phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas sras //
NK040(thi)014:1363: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs //
NK040(thi)014:1364: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa ma lus pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:1365: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK040(thi)014:1366: tshangs pa brgya byin rgyal chen bzhis //
NK040(thi)014:1367: mchod pa'i tshogs kyis rab mchod kyis //
NK040(thi)014:1368: nyin mtshan kun tu bsrung byed pa'i //
NK040(thi)014:1369: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK040(thi)014:1370: gnas 'dir nyin mo bde legs sogs /
NK040(thi)014:1371: de ltar 'grub par byed sogs ci rigs brjod /
NK040(thi)014:1373: des bdun pa gtor gzhong ma song /
NK040(thi)014:1375: thabs shes zung 'jug shin tu gces //
NK040(thi)014:1376: snang ba lam khyer de bas gces //
NK040(thi)014:1378: gong gi nyams len de rnams kyang /
NK040(thi)014:1379: pha rol tu phyin pa drug ldan gyis sgo nas nyams su len dgos te /
NK040(thi)014:1381: lus srog la ma chags par 'khor 'das thams cad mchod sbyin rgya chen bsngo ba ni sbyin pa /
NK040(thi)014:1382: mi dge ba la sogs sdig dang ma 'dres pa tshul khrims /
NK040(thi)014:1383: 'phang sems med cing sdug bsngal khyad du bsad pa bzod pa /
NK040(thi)014:1384: ma yengs pa rtse gcig tu byed pa bsam gtan te /
NK040(thi)014:1385: de bzhi thabs kyi nyams len yin la /
NK040(thi)014:1386: brtson 'grus ni thabs shes gnyis myur du bsgrub pa'i grogs yin cing /
NK040(thi)014:1387: shes rab ni mchod mkhan bdag /
NK040(thi)014:1389: mchod yul mgron bzhi la sogs pa thams cad sgyu
NK040(thi)014:1390: ma lta bur rang bzhin med par shes pa yin
NK040(thi)014:1391: te / re ba med pa sangs rgyas gcod //
NK040(thi)014:1392: dog pa med pas 'khor ba gcod //
NK040(thi)014:1393: nyams nga med pas 'dre bdud gcod //
NK040(thi)014:1395: gcod bya med pas kun kyang gcod //
NK040(thi)014:1397: zhib par 'og spyi ching gal mdo'i skabs su gsal lo //
NK040(thi)014:1398: gong gi nyams len de rnams zhag gcig gis nang thun drug gi sgo nas /
NK040(thi)014:1402: ri mgo'i nyi ma rtse shar dang gcig /
NK040(thi)014:1403: nyin phyed drang po dang gnyis /
NK040(thi)014:1404: grib chen 'dus pa dang gsum mo //
NK040(thi)014:1406: srod nam mkha' la skar ma shar ba dang gcig /
NK040(thi)014:1407: nam phyed drang po dang gnyis /
NK040(thi)014:1408: tho rang skar ma byer ba'i dus dang gsum mo //
NK040(thi)014:1409: gnyan sa min na nub re gcod thun re ma chags par byed do //
NK040(thi)014:1410: thun skabs rnams su btang len byed pa ni /
NK040(thi)014:1411: sems can thams cad kyi sdig sdug thams cad bdag la smin par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1412: bdag gi bde ba ma lus pa sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)014:1413: ces brjod pas rang la dngos su smin zhing gzhan
NK040(thi)014:1414: gyis dngos su thob pas sdig sdug thams cad dang
NK040(thi)014:1415: bral nas sangs rgyas thob par bsam ste /
NK040(thi)014:1417: gtong len gnyis po spel mar bya //
NK040(thi)014:1418: de nyid rlung la skyon de sbyangs //
NK040(thi)014:1419: yul gsum dug gsum dge ba gsum //
NK040(thi)014:1420: ces gsungs pa ltar yun ring du bsgom /
NK040(thi)014:1421: des mngon par rtogs pa'i rim pa song /
NK040(thi)014:1422: gdan thog gcig ma 'di ni chos grwa chen po
NK040(thi)014:1423: shar kahthoga rdo rje gdan gyi 'bangs su gyur pa'i
NK040(thi)014:1424: bya bral ba kun dga' 'bum gyis gnas mchog dam
NK040(thi)014:1425: pa 'phags mtsho'i ri khrod du sbyar ba'o ////
